            "title": "港股開升231點  阿里升近4%  山東黃金創歷史高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開報26861，升231點或0.87% ; 恒生科技指數開報5817，升55點或0.96% ; 恒生國企指數開報9201，升87點或0.96%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交47.92億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：山東黃金官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240712_FI_source-web_01787-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：山東黃金官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240712_FI_source-web_01787-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：山東黃金官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">山東黃金(01787)升3.96%，報47.28元，創歷史新高。紫金(02899)升1.3%，報40.54元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">腦動極光(06681)折讓12%配股，開跌6.28%，報5.97元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)升3.88%，報171.2元，成交居首，傳分拆晶片業務平頭哥獨立上市。小米(01810)公布購回股份，開升0.74%，報35.5元。騰訊(00700)報597.5元，無升跌</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">優必選(009880)組合資企業投資智能機器人，開升1.7%，報143.8元。<br/>   莊臣(01955)遭廉署搜查並拘捕3 名僱員，開跌1.79%，報0.55元。</p>\n</div>",
